(17, 2, '2009-03-04 04:03:58', 'Magento version 1.2.1.2 now available', 'Magento version 1.2.1.2 is now available for download and upgrade.\nThis version includes some updates to improve admin security as described in the release notes page.', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-version-1212-now-available/', 0, 0),
